    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "It's just everything. The doctor's visits, the pills, the way I can't even get out of this chair without a struggle. I used to be so independent, you know? Now I'm just... a burden. I'm just waiting for a phone call or a fall to finally end this cycle of decay. It feels like I've lost all my dignity.",
